meta.expressionLhs: CASE WHEN "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."USER_TYPE" = 'A' THEN 'Manual' WHEN "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."USER_TYPE" <> 'A' THEN 'Automated' WHEN ISNULL ( "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."USER_TYPE" ) = 1 THEN 'No User Specified' ELSE 'Other' END AS "User Type"

axis0.name: User Type
axis0.text:
CASE
    WHEN "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."USER_TYPE" = <%=manual_user_type%>
    THEN 'Manual'
    WHEN "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."USER_TYPE" != <%=manual_user_type%>
    THEN 'Automated'
    WHEN ISNULL("_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."USER_TYPE") = 1
    THEN 'No User Specified'
    ELSE 'Other'
END

variables.title: RatioPOValue
variables.variableValue:
SUM(CASE WHEN PU_FIRST("EKPO",ROUND_DAY("EKBE"."BUDAT"),"EKBE"."VGABE" = '2') <=
ROUND_DAY("EKPO"."AEDAT") 
THEN "EKPO"."NETWR"
ELSE 0.00
END) / SUM("EKPO"."NETWR")

variables.title: RatioPOItems
variables.variableValue:
SUM(CASE WHEN PU_FIRST("EKPO",ROUND_DAY("EKBE"."BUDAT"),"EKBE"."VGABE" = '2') <=
ROUND_DAY("EKPO"."AEDAT") 
THEN 1.00
ELSE 0.00
END) / COUNT_TABLE("EKPO")
